00:33:58,480 --> 00:34:07,360
Hrvatska, kao i svi ostali, imala bi koristi od ruskih turista i dobrobiti od dobrih odnosa s Rusijom i svih ostalih.

354
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:09,360
Imaju novca za potrošnju.

355
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:12,880
Hrvatska ima neke od najljepših mjesta na svijetu.

356
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:15,760
i tako bi ovo trebalo biti mirno mjesto.

357
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:26,960
Ne budite htjeli ući u ovu ludu spiralu nasilja i retorike i mržnje.

358
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,960
Nema podloge za to.

359
00:34:30,160 --> 00:34:32,080
Nema podloge za ono što se događa.

360
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:36,320
Rusija ne želi više zemlje.

361
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:41,680
Želi da se Sjedinjene Države poštuju i da ne ugrožavaju njezinu sigurnost.

362
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,840
To je ono što Rusija želi.

363
00:34:44,160 --> 00:34:48,960
A Rusija bi trebala dobiti to jer je to Amerika.

364
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,800
It's not doing me one whit of good.

365
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:56,160
It's only making my life more dangerous when NATO tries to expand.

366
00:34:56,880 --> 00:35:03,200
I'm sick of it too, because it just puts me under a nuklear risk that I don't want to be under.

367
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:11,360
To je jedini risk, by the way, the United States faces, no one's going to invade the United States, no one's going to attack the United States.

368
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:17,360
The only single security risk of the United States conceivable is a nuklear war.

369
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:21,520
So if they had a whit of sense about them, that's what they'd be trying to avoid.

370
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:24,480
Rather than saying, oh, Putin's call.

371
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:25,680
Moramo nas zvati blufom.

372
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:26,960
On samo blufira.

373
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:34,080
Ovi idioti, znate, žele provokirati do te mjere da, oh, oprostite, napravili smo pogrešku, na kojoj je to vrijeme svijet gotov.

374
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:37,200
Dakle, ovo je moj savjet za Hrvatsku.

375
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:42,800
Imate puno susjeda koji to shvaćaju, shvaćaju to, svi bi se trebali sastati.

376
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:57,600
Usput, čak je i Petar Pavel u Češkoj Republici, koji je bio NATO, pro NATO, pro NATO, nedavno rekao realistično, znate, Ukrajina ne može pobijediti u ovoj ratu.

377
00:35:57,680 --> 00:36:00,880
Dakle, u susjedstvu dolazi više zdravog razuma.

378
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:10,720
Uvijek je to učinjeno.

379
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:25,520
Hvala vam na pozornosti i vidimo se vrlo brzo.
